class Calculator:
    """Calculator in CLI which perform basic math operation.
    Future: Scientific Calculation will be added."""

    def __init__(self):
        pass

    # Addition
    def sum(self, a: int, b: int) -> int:
        """Perform addition between two given numbers.

        Parameters
        ----------
        a : int
            real integer number
        b : int
            real integer number

        Returns
        -------
        int
            real integer number
        """
        logger.info("Summing {a} and {b}")
        return a + b

    def substract(self, a: int, b: int) -> int:
        """Perform subtraction from first given number with second given number.

        Parameters
        ----------
        a : int
            real integer number
        b : int
            real integer number

        Returns
        -------
        int
            real integer number
        """
        logger.info("Substracing {a} and {b}")
        return a - b
